<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c2">(٦٧)</span> بابٌ: الْوَلِيمَةُ حَقٌّ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ عَبْدُ الرَّحْمَنِ بْنُ عَوْفٍ:</span> قالَ لِي النَّبِيُّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span>: <span class="c2">«أَوْلِمْ وَلَوْ بِشَاةٍ»</span>.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>